---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact Us" description="Book a free demo with Americall to discuss appointment-setting, campaign support, and calling operations.">
	<section class="grid-surface bg-ameri-navy px-5 py-20 text-white lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
			<div class="reveal">
				<p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Book a demo</p>
				<h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black leading-tight sm:text-5xl">Let's build a calling system that actually works.</h1>
				<p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-white/75">
					In a short demo call, Americall can walk you through how its calling, qualification, confirmation, and support process can fit your sales operation.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-8 rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 p-4 text-sm leading-6 text-white/75">
					Form backend is still a Phase 1 setup item. Connect Basin, Formspree, Getform, or a Cloudflare handler before launch.
				</p>
			</div>
			<form class="reveal rounded-md bg-white p-6 text-ameri-ink shadow-2xl shadow-black/25" method="post">
				<div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<label class="block">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-ameri-navy">First name</span>
						<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-md border border-ameri-border px-4 py-3 transition focus:border-ameri-red" name="firstName" autocomplete="given-name" required />
					</label>
					<label class="block">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-ameri-navy">Last name</span>
						<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-md border border-ameri-border px-4 py-3 transition focus:border-ameri-red" name="lastName" autocomplete="family-name" required />
					</label>
					<label class="block sm:col-span-2">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-ameri-navy">Company</span>
						<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-md border border-ameri-border px-4 py-3 transition focus:border-ameri-red" name="company" autocomplete="organization" required />
					</label>
					<label class="block sm:col-span-2">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-ameri-navy">Business email</span>
						<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-md border border-ameri-border px-4 py-3 transition focus:border-ameri-red" type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required />
					</label>
					<label class="block sm:col-span-2">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-ameri-navy">Contact number</span>
						<input class="mt-2 w-full rounded-md border border-ameri-border px-4 py-3 transition focus:border-ameri-red" type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" />
					</label>
					<label class="block sm:col-span-2">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-ameri-navy">How can Americall help?</span>
						<textarea class="mt-2 min-h-32 w-full rounded-md border border-ameri-border px-4 py-3 transition focus:border-ameri-red" name="message"></textarea>
					</label>
				</div>
				<button class="button-motion mt-6 w-full rounded-md bg-ameri-red px-6 py-3 text-sm font-black text-white hover:bg-red-700" type="submit">
					<span>Book a Free Demo</span>
				</button>
			</form>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
